## 1. Testing whether we can generate a sub dataset
Run:
```
docker run --rm -it -v $PWD:$PWD -v /home/rliu/projects/DeepCys/data/ABPP/atom3d_pdbs:/home/rliu/projects/DeepCys/data/ABPP/atom3d_pdbs -w $PWD gatr:latest /bin/bash
```
in the base directory of `geometric_algebra_transformer` and inside the container:
```
BASEDIR=/tmp/gatr-experiments && python scripts/generate_resprop_dataset.py base_dir="${BASEDIR}" seed=42 data.residues_file_path="scripts/resprop_tests/test.csv"
```
Alternatively, we can run locally in the `gatr-dev` conda environment. 
```
export CUDA_HOME=/home/rliu/software/cuda121
export LD_LIBRARY_PATH=/home/rliu/software/cuda121/lib64
BASEDIR=/tmp/gatr-experiments
BASEDIR=/tmp/gatr-experiments && python scripts/generate_resprop_dataset.py base_dir="${BASEDIR}" seed=42 data.residues_file_path="scripts/resprop_tests/test.csv"
```